- ## #retentionRate
##retentionRate #Retention #& #Churn #Customers #Value #Drivers #ValueBased #Software #Engineering #Software #Engineering 
The retention rate for period t (rt) is defined as the proportion of customers active at the end of period t–1 and still active at the end of period t
